It seems like attempting to destroy it would be risky due to its self-repair functions. And they can't just drop it into the sun (even under controlled circumstances) since the missile could potentially destroy it, or do some other form if irreparable damage. The best chance of neutralizing it without either Earth OR its target being destroyed is to find a world without intelligent life (preferably a barren rogue planet) and activate it there. NOT an easy task.





